Package edu.ucla.wise.admin

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminMonitorServlet
    AdminMonitorServlet class is used to load a new survey and set up its Data tables.
    AdminTestServlet
    AdminTestServlet class directs the user coming from email URL or interviewers to appropriate next step or page.
    AdminTool  
    AdminUserSession  
    CompleteServlet
    CompleteServlet Class is used to accept a hidden request from LOFTS to declare completion.
    Dev2ProdServlet
    Dev2ProdServlet class is used for converting the survey system from Development to production mode.
    DownloadFileServlet
    DownloadFileServlet is a class which is used when user tries to download survey data or preface or the survey questions from wise admin system.
    LoadDataServlet
    LoadDataServlet is a class which is used to load data into the system.
    LogonpServlet
    LogonpServlet is a class which is called when user tries to log into wise admin system, it also sets up AdminInfo in the admin user's session in case the user has logged in with valid credentials.
    LogonpServletTest
    Tests to check if the logonp servlet works.
    LogoutServlet
    LogoutServlet is a class which is called when admin user clicks on logout button, wise logs out of the admin page and goes back to log in page.
    PrintSurveyServlet
    PrintSurveyServlet is a class used when user tries to print the survey form wise admin system.
    ReloadServlet
    ReloadServlet class is used to load a new survey and set up its Data tables.
    SurveyResultServlet
    SurveyResultServlet is a class used when user tries to check the responses of people who have taken the survey.
    ViewSurveyServlet
    ViewSurveyServlet is a class used when user tries to check the survey form wise admin system.
    XsltViewServlet
    XsltViewServlet is a class used when user tries to print an overview list of the pages in a survey
